txt.en: The tower of Minas Rant can be found at the western end of the stream that cuts across the Norcrofts.\n\nThe number of Orcs remaining in the area has been reduced, due to your efforts.
A company of Orcs has taken to the ruins of the ancient tower, Minas Rant, and have begun to use it as an outpost from which to attack the neighbouring homes.
